It is a fashion week once again and two of the top models of the city have decided to be appeared on different fashion covers. They have fabulous style sense, but this time these two beauties are in hurry so they need your help. Would you come forward to give your helping hands to these two cuties? Join Outfit Competition and be prepared to guide them to prepare for the most popular photo shooting session!  Common friends! Their wardrobe is full of trendy outfits and matching accessories. 

You will play the role of fashion advisor in this brand new girls game. Try to take an action fast since these two famous models have very limited time to compete in this contest! Make sure to challenge your fashion abilities to the optimum level and dress them up to make look awesome. Choose the first girl and give her a nice blue color top with pink color flower or a grey color or a red and blue market with Barbie top and combine these upper outfits with the matching bottoms, including blue short with pink flower of blue or black color jeans. 

Make sure to complete their looks with the matching sandals that can improve their appearance amazingly. Try to be a little fast since the other princess is also waiting for her turn. Guide her as well to pick up the best outfits so that she can have the amazing look for this specific event! Every girl participated in the contest is going to give their best, so it is your duty to help these girls to secure the best place in this popular dress up completion.
